# AI Dev Framework — infrastructure (pulled from framework repo, not committed)
# Project knowledge files travel across devs (plans, handoffs, plan-impl reports,
# context, config, lessons, roadmap). Per-dev / framework-shipped files don't.
.ai/*
!.ai/PROJECT_CONFIG.md
!.ai/PROJECT_LESSONS.md
!.ai/ROADMAP.md
!.ai/context/
!.ai/plans/
!.ai/handoffs/
!.ai/reports/
.ai/reports/*/
!.ai/reports/plan-implementation/
.ai/plans/.*
.ai/handoffs/.*
.ai/reports/plan-implementation/.*
.claude/
.agent/
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
.cursorrules
.windsurfrules
.clinerules
.github/copilot-instructions.md
